    1. A user can begin a game
    2. When an user begins a game then the user sees an introductory explanation and a button to continue to the first clue
    3. When an user presses the button to continue to the first clue the game begins and he sees the first clue
    4. When the user hits the clue he goes to next clue
    5. When the user hits the last clue It wins the game
    6. When the user wins the game, a congratulation text will be shown with a button "get the gift"
    7. When the user presses the button "get the gift", the prize won will be shown with the score obtained
    8. The clue will be of 3 types: Choose the options, write the answer or be in the right place
    9. When choosing the option clue is shown, the user must choose between three options
    10. The options for "choose the option" will be texts or images
    11. A user that hits a clue of "choose the option" get 10X points if he hits in first try, 3X if he hits in second try, and X if hitting at the third try
    12. When "write the answer" clue is shown, the user must write the correct answer
    13. When "be in the right place" clue is shown, the user must write the geographical coordinates or be in the right place and share the device gps
    14. When a user is in a clue a countdown will be activated
    15. When a user is X time in a clue a tip help will be show to resolve the clue
    16. The tip to resolve "choose an option" will remove a not valid option
    17. The tip for "write the answer" will be showning some letters
    18. The tip for "be in the right place" will be showning the longitude

    
   Not Functional
    1. The Api must implement http and http/2
    2. The service for tips help must be a type Push or queue protocol
    3. The system must hold on 50 concurrent user in 24/7
    4. The system must be split in microservices in Kubernetes 
    5. A stress test should be made with tools like SoapUI, Jmeter or other 
    6. The user data and game information should be persisted in a guaranteed security system
